name: TheAlly's Wholesome Grannies
description:
The embedding you've all been waiting for - Wholesome Grannies! We all (I hope) have fond memories of our grandmother, baking in her kitchen, or out milking her cow, or singing hymns at her piano. Good times!

This is a lovely, wholesome, embed. No funny business.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
